        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "I was on the platform just then.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "After determining our position, the captain pronounced only these words:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "He went down the hatch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "I returned to the lounge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "Some minutes later it stopped at a depth of eight hundred thirty three meters and came to rest on the seafloor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "The ceiling lights in the lounge then went out, the panels opened, and through the windows I saw, for a half mile radius, the sea brightly lit by the beacon's rays.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "I looked to port and saw nothing but the immenseness of these tranquil waters.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "What ship was this?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-839_130898_000059_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/839/130898/839_130898_000059_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-839",
        "content": "On july fourth seventeen seventy nine, as a member of the squadron under Admiral d'Estaing, it assisted in the capture of the island of Grenada.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
